Product Description

Excellent Audio Companion for Your iPhone

UGREEN Lightning Earbuds are MFi certified (UPC/EAN: 6957303886555). It means there won’t be any error message or something strange popping up on your iOS device, seamlessly with any of your iPhone, iPad, iPod which features a Lightning port.

Feel the Beat, Feel the Music

Compared with traditional 3.5mm audio transfer, it provides lossless signal transmission of 24-bit digital audio with the encoding and playback of music, higher sampling rates than the standards used in CDs, makes you feel like you are at the concert with the band.

Ultra Comfort

S/M/L three sizes of silicone earplugs are included for a customized fit in your ears and improved noise isolation.

You can comfortably enjoy music with it for a long time while going on a journey, studying in the library, or workout at the gym, etc.

10mm Dynamic Driver

10mm dynamic driver in this lightning earbuds provides higher sensitivity, achieves amazing high-resolution sound reproduction.

Ergonomic Design

45° into the ear, ergonomically designed shape design. High-quality alloy earphone shell brings a more comfortable listening experience.

Top-notch Microphone

Features with advanced Knowles microphone, effectively filter current noise, restore pure sound quality, and enjoy ultra-clear calls.

Durable Cable

Built-in 5-strand 6-core bullet-proof silk wire, more flexible and effective against stretching, offers a long-last life even in heavy use.

Muti-Function In-Line Control

For iPod touch (7th generation), iPod touch (6th generation)

Volume+: Short press “+”

Volume-: Short press “-”

Answer/End a Call: Single press Centre Button

Decline a Call: Press and hold Centre Button

Wake up Siri: Press and hold Centre Button until hearing a voice prompt then release

Play/Pause: Single press Centre Button

Next Track: Double press Centre Button

Previous Track: Triple press Centre Button

Fast-forward: Double-press Centre Button and hold on the second press

Fast-backwards: Triple-Press Centre Button and hold on the third press
